The paper introduces a Python module for cluster-distributed multi-dimensional numerical arrays, which is relevant to distributed computing (cs.DC) and numerical analysis (cs.NA). The module also involves data structures (cs.DS) and software engineering (cs.SE) aspects. Additionally, the paper discusses the performance of the module, which could be relevant to measurement and analysis (cs.MS).
